				{
					"dataType": "talent",
					"elementDisplay": "<p chunk_id=\"bae144a0-0e74-459b-8056-bdf3398323a3\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-stat\"><strong><span class=\"color-span\">Prerequisite:</span></strong> Speak the First Ideal</p>\n<p chunk_id=\"4f526983-f5b9-4720-919c-96225bc38a27\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-stat\"><strong><span class=\"color-span\">Act</span></strong><strong><span class=\"color-span\">ivation:</span></strong> <span aria-label=\"Always Active\" class=\"icon-font icon\" title=\"Always Active\">∞</span></p>\n<div chunk_id=\"e9ff5c29-dd2b-42a6-8beb-934f83aa9ff7\" class=\"lore-block\" style=\"\">\n<p class=\"\"><em>You become increasingly adept at using Abrasion to glide through your environment.</em></p>\n</div>\n<p chunk_id=\"2be3cd90-71a4-433a-927b-0c908367fe24\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-body\">While <tooltip category=\"rule\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"surge-infusions-and-durations\" nexus=\"cosmererpg\">infused with</tooltip>\n<tooltip category=\"action\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"abrasion-surge\" nexus=\"cosmererpg\">Abrasion</tooltip>, your movement rate increases by 10 feet, and you ignore the <tooltip category=\"condition\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"slowed\" nexus=\"cosmererpg\">Slowed</tooltip> condition when imposed by <tooltip category=\"rule\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"difficult-terrain\" nexus=\"cosmererpg\">difficult terrain</tooltip>, <tooltip category=\"rule\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"climbing-crawling-and-swimming\" nexus=\"cosmererpg\">climbing, crawling, and swimming</tooltip>.</p>",
