					"_highlightResult": {
						"elementDisplay": {
							"value": "<p chunk_id=\"cf2b8a1f-afad-40e7-bbc7-d515c1bb673d\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-stat\"><strong><span class=\"color-span\">Prerequisite:</span></strong> <tooltip category=\"talent\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"frictionless-motion\" nexus=\"cosmererpg\">Frictionless Motion</tooltip> talent</p>\n<p chunk_id=\"09a99e6b-b58a-436b-8ff8-812a0f12ff63\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-stat\"><strong><span class=\"color-span\">Act</span></strong><strong><span class=\"color-span\">ivation:</span></strong> <span aria-label=\"Always Active\" class=\"icon-font icon\" title=\"Always Active\">∞</span></p>\n<div chunk_id=\"e7571dac-23b2-4cf7-aa67-1237eb748162\" class=\"lore-block\" style=\"\">\n<p class=\"\"><em>You dynamically skate around the battlefield, easily slipping away from your foes.</em></p>\n</div>\n<p chunk_id=\"584ec774-0bae-4569-89f8-1c219ac7c2df\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-body\">When you Skate, you aren’t restricted to moving in a straight line.</p>",
