					"_highlightResult": {
						"elementDisplay": {
							"value": "<p chunk_id=\"94d92c56-63bb-487f-ae5e-5bfd08cb5c69\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-stat\"><strong><span class=\"color-span\">Prerequisite:</span></strong> <tooltip category=\"talent\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"slippery-target\" nexus=\"cosmererpg\">Slippery Target</tooltip> talent</p>\n<p chunk_id=\"9d84e205-fad0-48e5-a64b-ab043dff998f\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-stat\"><strong><span class=\"color-span\">Act</span></strong><strong><span class=\"color-span\">ivation:</span></strong> <span aria-label=\"Special Activation\" class=\"icon-font icon\" title=\"Special Activation\">★</span></p>\n<div chunk_id=\"68c94d2e-abda-4d76-a3de-feef37555045\" class=\"lore-block\" style=\"\">\n<p class=\"\"><em>You are poetry in motion, able to perform nearly any feat without slowing down.</em></p>\n</div>\n<p chunk_id=\"b259b0cb-3072-474e-9313-7e16257f776a\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-body\">When you Skate or otherwise <tooltip category=\"action\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"move\" nexus=\"cosmererpg\">Move</tooltip> while infused with Abrasion, you can interrupt your movement at one or more points, use other actions as if you’d finished your Move, then use your remaining movement as if you were still in the middle of that Move action.</p>\n<p chunk_id=\"9fc63a6c-0cd6-41e2-a735-5110c4ee92c5\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-body\">Once per round, when you make a melee weapon attack after starting that Move but before finishing it, you can roll an extra 1d4 damage for that attack. The size of this die increases with your ranks in Abrasion: at 2 ranks, roll an extra 1d6 damage (instead of 1d4), and so on. However, if you add this damage die, the GM can spend <span aria-label=\"Complication\" class=\"icon-font-red icon\" title=\"Complication\">C</span> from the attack test to cause you to fall <tooltip category=\"condition\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"prone\" nexus=\"cosmererpg\">Prone</tooltip> and immediately end your Move action.</p>",
							"matchLevel": "none",
							"matchedWords": []
						},
						"name": {
							"value": "Slick Combatant",
							"matchLevel": "none",
							"matchedWords": []
						},
						"shortDescription": {
							"value": "While infused with Abrasion, you can interrupt a Move with other actions.",
							"matchLevel": "none",
							"matchedWords": []
						}
					}
				},
				{
					"dataType": "talent",
					"elementDisplay": "<p chunk_id=\"59a30224-c554-44a6-be0b-368cb784ce5f\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-stat\"><strong><span class=\"color-span\">Prerequisite:</span></strong>\n<tooltip category=\"talent\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"graceful-skating\" nexus=\"cosmererpg\">Graceful Skating</tooltip> talent\n</p>\n<p chunk_id=\"0c834fec-ecdf-42f6-a4c9-f06a0800f15e\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-stat\"><strong><span class=\"color-span\">Act</span></strong><strong><span class=\"color-span\">ivation:</span></strong> <span aria-label=\"Always Active\" class=\"icon-font icon\" title=\"Always Active\">∞</span></p>\n<div chunk_id=\"e331c974-237b-44a1-a790-cb4a2ae957a1\" class=\"lore-block\" style=\"\">\n<p class=\"\"><em>You make yourself so slick that glancing and hasty blows slide right off you.</em></p>\n</div>\n<p chunk_id=\"5c7b89f3-a211-4038-8889-e79d037a3db9\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-body\">While you are infused with Abrasion, attacks can’t <tooltip category=\"rule\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"graze\" nexus=\"cosmererpg\">graze</tooltip> you and <tooltip category=\"action\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"reactive-strike\" nexus=\"cosmererpg\">Reactive Strikes</tooltip> against you gain a <tooltip category=\"rule\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"advantages-and-disadvantages\" nexus=\"cosmererpg\">disadvantage</tooltip>.</p>",
