				{
					"dataType": "talent",
					"elementDisplay": "<p chunk_id=\"65b81b25-eb15-49c6-99aa-b87524d97af1\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-stat ParaOverride-2\"><strong><span class=\"color-span\">Prerequisite:</span></strong>\n<tooltip category=\"talent\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"distant-surgebinding\" nexus=\"cosmererpg\">Distant Surgebinding</tooltip> talent or <tooltip category=\"talent\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"slippery-target\" nexus=\"cosmererpg\">Slippery Target</tooltip> talent\n</p>\n<p chunk_id=\"f90268f7-a6ff-47af-a02f-0a2b304301c7\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-stat\"><strong><span class=\"color-span\">Act</span></strong><strong><span class=\"color-span\">ivation:</span></strong> <span aria-label=\"Always Active\" class=\"icon-font icon\" title=\"Always Active\">∞</span></p>\n<div chunk_id=\"26324c3f-82c1-4f9b-9b78-753c8f32d481\" class=\"lore-block\" style=\"\">\n<p class=\"\"><em>You’ve become so efficient at infusing yourself with Abrasion that it becomes subconscious, allowing you to slip around with effortless grace.</em></p>\n</div>\n<p chunk_id=\"a41d9921-567a-4692-b17e-5824d107395d\" class=\"CORE-paragraph-styles_CORE-body ParaOverride-2\">While you have 1 <tooltip category=\"rule\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"investiture\" nexus=\"cosmererpg\">Investiture</tooltip> or more, you gain the benefits of being <tooltip category=\"rule\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"surge-infusions-and-durations\" nexus=\"cosmererpg\">infused with</tooltip> Abrasion without spending Investiture, and it costs you 1 fewer <tooltip category=\"rule\" class=\"tooltip-convert\" element=\"focus\" nexus=\"cosmererpg\">focus</tooltip> to Skate.</p>",
